## Fractal App Features

### **💬 Chat **
- Private Telegram group chat with your Circle
- This conversation is private and will not be stored.
- Stay on topic—focus on the proposals!

### **📊 Fractal App Buttons & Navigation**

**Proposal Cards:**
- See all comments and votes
- Add your own comment
- Cast your vote

**Rep Voting Card:**
- Shows Circle members
- Shows final representatives and their medals (at the end)
- Allocate your Gold/Silver/Bronze votes here

