## Tips for Great Participation

### **Before the Round Starts**
✅ Read the Fractal topic carefully
✅ Think about what matters most to you
✅ Introduce yourself in the Circle chat
✅ Share your ideas and get some feedback.

### **During Proposal Phase**
✅ Ask clarifying questions in comments
✅ Build on others' ideas
✅ Rate comments that add real value
✅ Keep proposals focused and specific
✅ Use clear language—avoid jargon

### **During Voting Phase**
✅ Vote on **all** proposals
✅ Vote based on **merit**, not friendship
✅ Think about what's truly best for the group
✅ Be fair—use the full 1-10 scale
✅ Choose your representative for their **integrity and understanding**, not popularity

### **General Best Practices**
✅ Stay respectful and constructive
✅ Listen to different perspectives
✅ Vote honestly—it matters!
✅ Don't spam or post off-topic messages
✅ If you disagree, use comments to explain your thinking

