## Summary: Your Fractal Journey

1. ✅ ** → Get added to a Circle
2. ✅ **Propose & Discuss** → Share ideas, add comments, rate feedback
3. ✅ **Vote** → Score proposals (1-10), choose a representative (Gold/Silver/Bronze)
4. ✅ **Advance (if selected)** → Move to next round
5. ✅ **Repeat** → Until final results
6. ✅ **View Results** → See winning ideas and decision history

**The goal:** Leverage the wisdom of the whole group to surface the best ideas and select thoughtful representatives at each level.

